**Classic Game Requirements**


1) The game shall allow the player to control a snake that moves continuously within the play area.

2) The snake shall change direction in response to player input.

3) The snake shall move at a constant speed that increases as the game progresses (increase difficulty).

4) The snake shall grow in length when it consumes food.

5) The game shall end when the snake collides with itself.

6) The game shall end when the snake collides with the boundary of the play area.

7) Food shall appear at a valid location that is not occupied by the snake.

8) Only one piece of food shall be present at a time.

9) The game shall increase the playerâ€™s score each time food is consumed.

10) The game shall display the current score during gameplay.

**New Features**

1) have invincebility tokens randomly pop up temporarly where the snake shall pass through itself and not be harmed for 30 seconds.

2) Have rare "super food" appear that awards significant bonus points and disappears quickly. 

3) "Rats" shall pop up that spawn and move towards the boundry of the play area before disappearing. They move slower than the snake. Twice as many points as food. 

4) temporary "slow motion" tokens pop up temporarly at high scores that slow the speed of gameplay. 
